        (8226, 'Billie Whitelaw', '1932-06-06', 'Billie Honor Whitelaw, CBE  was an English actress of both stage and film. She worked in close collaborration with Irish playwright Samuel Beckett for 25 years and wass regarded as one of the foremost interpreters of his works. She was also known for her portrayal of Mrs Baylock, the demonic nanny in The Omen.', 'Coventry, England', 1, '/5XSUS3oSuG2CtJQPiEBQd9AAmg4.jpg'),
