Description above from the Wikipedia article Warren Oates, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 'Depoy, Kentucky, USA', 2, '/qgelB9xOkMDLf2sDQH5XfVPh29K.jpg'),
