Description above from the Wikipedia article Anne Heche, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 'Aurora, Ohio, USA', 2, '/eY3cgIQR4ao1fqCMvxrdcR0nyt0.jpg'),
