        (8309, 'Kierston Wareing', '1978-01-07', 'Kierston Wareing is an English actress. Her first film role was the lead in Ken Loach''s It''s a Free World..., followed by a supporting role in Andrea Arnold''s Fish Tank – which won the BAFTA award for "Best British Film" and the Jury Prize at the Cannes Film Festival. Wikipedia', 'Leigh-on-Sea, Essex, England, UK', 1, '/lcPlix0o1cQxOWG0YbeshdvGzfj.jpg'),
