In later years, Hamilton made frequent cameo appearances on television sitcoms and commercials. She also gained recognition for her work as an advocate of causes designed to benefit children and animals, and retained a lifelong commitment to public education.', 'Cleveland, Ohio, USA', 1, '/vZhqGZoHnj3HoVDg1HFGVf3c197.jpg'),
