Description above from the Wikipedia article Helen Hunt, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 'Los Angeles, California, USA', 4, '/ws1ClG9BBUIVLZRYTNKconJn9Sy.jpg'),
