Description above from the Wikipedia article Geoffrey Palmer , licensed under CC-BY-SA,full list of contributors on Wikipedia.    ', 'London, England, UK', 1, '/6ouSoFGy8Rd9viyHmWHoEJfknFa.jpg'),
