        (10952, 'Lorenzo Di Bonaventura', NULL, 'Di Bonaventura is best known for being the President of Worldwide Production for Warner Bros. Pictures. Di Bonaventura had been an executive at Warner Bros. since the 1990s. During his tenure at Warner Bros. he has discovered and shepherded many blockbuster movies.  Di Bonaventura is responsible bringing pop culture classics The Matrix and Harry Potter, among others to the big screen. Di Bonaventura also owns his own production company called Di Bonaventura Pictures and is based at Paramount Pictures.', NULL, 1, '/2HjxJv0FbdJtlIqNniU0h36LYGw.jpg'),
