        (11022, 'Aaron Stanford', '1976-12-27', 'Aaron Stanford (born December 27, 1976 height 5'' 7½" (1,71 m)) is an American actor best known for his roles as Pyro in X2 and X-Men: The Last Stand, and Doug in the 2006 remake of The Hills Have Eyes. From 2010 to 2013, he starred as Birkhoff in Nikita.

