        (14468, 'Brian Glover', '1934-04-02', 'Brian Glover was an English character actor, writer and wrestler. Glover was a professional wrestler (as ''Leon Arras the Man From Paris''), teacher, and finally a film, television and stage actor, and the voice of Tetley Tea. He was married to writer Tara Prem from 1954 until his death in 1997.', 'Sheffield, South Yorkshire, England, UK', 1, '/w9pZoousAMR2CylpxRSmJ0Cw78Z.jpg'),
