        (16304, 'Brian Koppelman', '1966-04-27', 'Brian Koppelman is an American screenwriter, novelist, director, and producer. Best known as the co-writer of Ocean''s Thirteen, and Rounders, Koppelman has also produced films such as The Illusionist and The Lucky Ones as well as directed films such as Solitary Man.

