Description above from the Wikipedia article Zero Mostel, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 'Brooklyn, New York, USA', 1, '/3EexCCgqsUSj6ObFpZ75sXFCJLX.jpg'),
